title: Dakine Explorer 26L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Explorer 26L Pack in Portway.
Features: 
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Skateboard carry straps
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Mesh side pockets
- Adjustable sternum strap
